{"tid":1548310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"昂坪市集有活動！！！","createTime":"2019-09-07T03:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T04:02:26.000Z","uid":23752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"aaf7885effc64c52d50d634fb4ce018256e7fdce","tid":1548310,"uid":23752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:40:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人近期壓力好大好抑鬱 所以大家不如就趁放假去放鬆下啦 下面有少少活動詳情比大家記一記 到時比人問起去邊玩都唔會口啞啞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋呢幾日天氣咁熱 冇咩事都唔好著黑色衫喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n韓國打卡展<br />\n韓國人氣景點Instasia拍照館首次來港！打造室內5個以「Chill-cool花園」為主題的佈景空間，讓賓客盡情拍照！<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年7月12 日至9月15日<br />\n時間：上午10時30分至下午4時50分 (平日) ; 上午10時至下午5時20分 (星期六、日)<br />\n地點：昂坪市集360旅遊資訊中心側<br />\n入場時間：每節20分鐘<br />\n入場方法：賓客出示任何一張昂坪360門票，即可免費進入韓國打卡展﹗每日名額有限，先到先得。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.np360.com.hk/tc/events-promotions/events/chill-cool-summer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.np360.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fevents-promotions%2Fevents%2Fchill-cool-summer&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=2c0717fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.np360.com.hk/tc/events-promotions/events/chill-cool-summer</a>"},{"pid":"d15d566e75e81be1dee8865817299d8c97ed20cc","tid":1548310,"uid":23752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:41:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3760810675aef6e6d8671dd16fffa71b0103651","tid":1548310,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:41:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63dd053bfe8b5a00ef6200ade7867a406004a21d","tid":1548310,"uid":23752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:41:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65d7cb89422da81f3dc0c926f9e7bd756cea635e","tid":1548310,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:41:20.000Z"